### How to Use:
1. Open your email client (such as Gmail, Outlook, etc.).
2. Start composing a new email.
3. Look for an option to insert HTML (in some clients, you may need to open the raw HTML view).
4. Paste the HTML code provided above.
5. Fill in the email addresses as needed and send!

Feel free to modify the text or styling as necessary!

